hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Can I call you back? can you get permethrin 5 over the counter "If someone comes to you with a problem surely you would be trying to fix the thing that is actually causing their problem. That person's worry is that they can't see their doctor. Is it really genuinely the case that everybody in that waiting area is an immigrant with no right to be here? I think it's pretty unlikely. So you need to deal with the problem that people want you to fix, rather than just reacting to what people are immediately saying. Otherwise, it's just going to get worse, and it becomes this self-fulfilling prophecy."
